`C-c C-s C-a'
`M-x rmail-sort-by-author'
     Sort messages of current Rmail buffer by author's name.

`C-c C-s C-r'
`M-x rmail-sort-by-recipient'
     Sort messages of current Rmail buffer by recipient's names.

`C-c C-s C-c'
`M-x rmail-sort-by-correspondent'
